### Test Guest System
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1

### 1. Create Guest
POST {{baseUrl}}/guests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ahmed.hassan@example.com",
  "fullName": "Ahmed Hassan",
  "phone": "+201234567890",
  "locale": "en"
}

### 2. Get Guest by SessionId (replace with sessionId from step 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/guests/REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID

### 3. Get Guest by Email
GET {{baseUrl}}/guests/email/ahmed.hassan@example.com

### 4. Update Guest
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/guests/REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Ahmed Hassan Updated",
  "phone": "+201234567899"
}

### 5. Extend Expiration
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/guests/REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID/extend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "daysToAdd": 15
}

### 6. Get Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/guests/statistics

### 7. Get All Guests
GET {{baseUrl}}/guests

### 8. Delete Guest
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/guests/REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID
